law.history: Repealed 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 226, sec. 113, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 225, sec. 3, effective June 17, 1978. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 114, sec. 8. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 58, sec. 15, effective March 5, 1952.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Local mutual aid arrangements -- Assistance in negotiation of reciprocal agreements with adjoining states or their political subdivisions.
